dct_description_sm: Maps generally show administrative boundaries, population of towns, road materials, road conditions, airfields, bridges, water features. Each map includes inset: "Schedion Poleōs 1:20,000 = Town Plan 1:20,000." Each map includes inset: "Σχεδίον πόλεως 1:20,000 = Town Plan 1:20,000." Title devised by cataloger. Princeton University Library map collection has 23 out of 54 prefectures or nomoi (according to pre-1999 administrative divisions of Greece). Some maps show sheet number on lower right margin.
dct_publisher_sm: Athēnai : Ministry of Public Works - Public Roads Administration, [1945-1951].
